data.description: $15,000 CONCESSION OFFERED BY SELLER FOR LIMITED TIME! Everything you've been looking for in MVISD! This 2304 sqft home in the wonderful subdivision of Country Village features 4 bedrooms, 2 full baths, an office, two living areas, a large kitchen, and a pool, all on a corner lot! House features many updates such as recently replaced roof, water heater, HVAC and all new landscape and irrigation system. This home has been meticulously maintained and cared for and ready for its new owner! You'll fall in love with all this home has to offer. Come take a look!
